---
// Testimonials section
---

<section class="section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto container-padding">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
      <h2 class="text-h1 text-charcoal mb-4">Trusted by Data Teams</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        See what data professionals are saying about BaseOut
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="testimonial-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">
          "BaseOut transformed our data management. We went from worrying about data loss to confidently scaling our Airtable operations."
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">Sarah Chen</div>
        <div class="testimonial-company">VP of Operations, TechFlow</div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">
          "The analytics capabilities are incredible. We're getting insights from our Airtable data that we never thought possible."
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">Marcus Rodriguez</div>
        <div class="testimonial-company">Data Analyst, Growth Labs</div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">
          "Finally, enterprise-grade governance for Airtable. BaseOut made our compliance audit a breeze."
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">Jennifer Walsh</div>
        <div class="testimonial-company">CISO, SecureData Inc</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 